item.description: I am a third year Ph.D. Student under the supervision of Dr. Jing Gao in Department of Computer Science and Engineering, The State University of New York at Buffalo. Before joining UB in 2016, I got my Master of Science degree in Statistics from University of California, San Diego and got my Bachelor of Science degree in Mathematics from Shandong University.
